itemDescription: son of Charles FitzRoy, 10th Duke of Grafton (1919-2011)

wikipedia_page.main: Hugh Denis Charles FitzRoy, 11th Duke of Grafton  (3 April 1919 – 7 April 2011) was the son of Charles FitzRoy, 10th Duke of Grafton, and his first wife Lady Doreen Maria Josepha Sydney Buxton, second daughter of Sydney Buxton, 1st Earl Buxton. He was known from 1936 to 1970 as the Earl of Euston.
